Reality television has opened the doors for countless celebs, but many of them got their true start as music video leads. 
Whether it be the stars of Real Housewives of Atlanta , Love & Hip Hop , Basketball Wives or any number of shows, these gorgeous gals were on the rise before many of their mainstream followers knew who they were! 
Check out these reality stars that’ve doubled as video vixens above.
